# Docker Networking vs Kubernetes Networking

| Docker | Kubernetes |
|----------|------------|
| Bridge Network | CNI Plugin (Calico, Cilium, etc.) |
| Container IP | Pod IP |
| Port Mapping (-p) | Kubernetes Service |
| Docker Network | Kubernetes Cluster Network |

Once applications are deployed to Kubernetes, networking is handled by Kubernetes rather than Docker.

